{
  "stem": "21319.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, the crematorium used to burn the dead bodies wasn't working anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was big, big mountains of dead bodies laying, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One, two, three, four.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only thing what I saw is dead bodies and people crawling around on all four like little mice, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they were flabbergasted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were-- they couldn't see it move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grass.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The-- you see, the-- the Nazis had a kitchen where they used to cook for the people there, for the Nazis, for-- so we used to find sleeves of potatoes peels, you know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it was no-- no food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why everybody was dying, from diseases and no food. 16,000 people died after the liberation, or 17,000, in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They have-- everything is taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like-- they treated us-- treated me like a little child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They burned down-- they-- after seven-- six-- because it was all the-- the diseases, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they burned down Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wipe even it out with the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they moved out to Bergen-Belsen, which is where the German Nazis stay, where the-- the soldiers were in, like regular barracks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where they moved the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and Belsen was completely liquidated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Burned down to the ground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She's doing this on purpose, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That woman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you try after the war to go home at all, to-- to look for family members?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To home?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I know everybody was dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hohne.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The original camp Bergen-Belsen was wiped out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed in part of Bergen-Belsen where the German soldiers and military, [GERMAN] house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that time, I worked for UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
